Package com.earth2me.essentials.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAsyncTeleport
    Manages EssentialsX's teleport functionality for a player.
    II18n Deprecated.
    External plugins should prefer to use either the player's client language (Player.getLocale() or II18n in case of future additions.
    IItemDb Deprecated.
    External plugins should use IItemDb instead, which includes access to IItemDb.ItemResolver APIs.
    IJails Deprecated.
    External plugins should use IJails instead of this interface in case future APIs are added.
    IReload Deprecated.
    This is a remnant of the abandoned 3.x storage system.
    ITeleport Deprecated.
    This API is not asynchronous and is no longer maintained.
    IWarps Deprecated.
    External plugins should use IWarps instead of this interface, in case future APIs are added.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Economy
    You should use Vault instead of directly using this class.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidNameException Deprecated.
    This exception relates to the abandoned 3.x storage refactor and is not implemented.
    InvalidWorldException Deprecated.
    This exception is unused.
    NoLoanPermittedException
    Thrown when a user does not have the balance for a transaction and cannot take a loan.
    UserDoesNotExistException
    Thrown when the requested user does not exist.
